this is linux port of nehe's lesson22
this port is done in 1 day, if you like
this port or if you correct a bug,
mail me at lucriz@inwind.it

to build lesson22 you need SDL-1.1.6 or better,
and, of course, an opengl implementation for linux
like mesa (www.mesa3d.org).

for building the binary executable
run:

./configure

at the end of configure script run make.

happy lesson22